## 💳 Razorpay Integration

- PDF download button on Kundali result page
- Amount: ₹5 (500 paise)
- Uses `NEXT_PUBLIC_RAZORPAY_KEY` env variable
- Loads checkout dynamically, generates text PDF on success

## 📍 Location System

- Free Open-Meteo geocoding API
- Debounced autocomplete dropdown
- Returns: city name, state, country, latitude, longitude, timezone
- Used in: Kundali, Matching, Remedies forms

## 🚀 To Deploy

```bash
npm run dev          # Development
npm run build        # Production build  
# Deploy to Vercel → point vivaai.in domain
```

### Environment Variables (.env.local)
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_RAZORPAY_KEY=rzp_test_xxxxx  # Add your key
```
